high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the stove.
Pick up the knife on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn left to face the potato on the counter.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Face the counter above the potato.
Place the knife on the counter by the sliced potato.
Look down to face the potato on the counter.
Pick up a slice of potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward and then turn left to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice and then remove it from the microwave.
Turn right and step forward to face the sink.
Place the slice of potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of potato and place it in the sink.

high_descs: turn around and move forward towards the stove
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle that is to the left of the stove top
turn to the left to face the counter with the potato
slice the potato with the knife
move back slightly from the counter
put the knife on to the counter on top of the spatula
face the counter in front of the potato
pick up a slice of potato from the counter
turn around and move forward, passing the stove on the left to the counter on the right side of the stove with the microwave, turn to face the microwave
open the microwave door, put the potato slice in to the microwave, close the door, cook for three seconds, open the door, remove the potato and close the door
turn to the right to face the sink
put the slice of potato in to the sink
anns.task_desc: put a cooked potato slice in to the sink

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter near the stove
Pick up a knife from the counter
Turn to the potato on the counter
Cut the potato into slices
Look back up at the counter
Put the knife on the counter
Look back down at the potato
Pick up a slice of potato
Go to the microwave
Heat the potato slice in the microwave
Turn to the sink
Put the cooked potato slice in the sink
anns.task_desc: Cook a potato slice and place it in the sink
